name: voucherEntryImportCSVFile

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to Voucher Entry page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Voucher Entries,Voucher Entry}

testSteps.description: Then the Payment Information form and its contents should show up
When I set the Supplier to '133339'
When I set the 'Invouce Number' to 'HjBludNqAy'
When I set the Currency to 'USD'
When i click on continue button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
When I set the Gross Amount to '15000'
When i click on continue button
Then the 'GL Distribution' form and its contents should show up

When I generate a GL Distribution csv file with a single row with value: Account Number: 'X.911000', Amount: <Balance amount>, Line Description: 'Test', Employee: '31578', Cost Center: 'MAN5000', Gen Obj: 'AFGHAIGEACT0', AOE: 'YAO-25005', Units: '10', Unit of Measure: '1' Project ID: 'APS-0001'
When i import a GL distribution csv file

Then the first GL Distribution line should contain: Account Number: 'X.911000', Amount: <Previous balance amount>, Line Description: 'Test', Employee: '31578', Cost Center: 'MAN5000', Gen Obj: 'AFGHAIGEACT0', AOE: 'YAO-25005', Units: '10', Unit of Measure: '1' Project ID: 'APS-0001'

children.description: Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain account number 'X.911000'
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain amount '15000.00'
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain line description 'Test'
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain employee '31578'
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain cost center 'MAN5000'
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain general obj 'AFGHAIGEACT0'
When I click on the 'Show Next' button
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain AOE id 'YAO-25005'
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain units '10'
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain unit of measure '1'
Then the GL Distribution Line '0' should contain project id 'APS-0001'

testSteps.description: Then the voucher entry successfully created modal and its contents should show up

children.description: Then the voucher entry successfully created modal should show up

exception.message: Expected condition failed: waiting for visibility of element located by By.xpath: //div[contains(@class, 'modal') and contains(@style, 'left: 0px')]//h3 (tried for 20 second(s) with 100 milliseconds interval)

children.description: Then the batch number from voucher entry successfully created modal should show up
Then the document number from voucher entry successfully created modal should show up
